<div class="title">A Christmas Story</div>
<div class="substance">Amanita muscaria</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Miles+X&Exact=1">Miles X</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Miles X. "A Christmas Story: An Experience with Amanita muscaria (exp40339)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Dec 25, 2015. erowid.org/exp/40339</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
